        <num>47-4-27</num>
        <content>
          <p>The board may take any gift, grant, or bequest, any money, any real or personal property, or any other thing of value and hold or invest the same for the uses and purposes of the retirement system, in accordance with this chapter.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1969, p. 998, ยง 15.)</p>
